1.title: Summer Abroad

episode of.title: The Most Popular Girls in School (TV Series 2012– )

1.plot: After a boring summer Mackenzie is contacted by Jeanie Halverstad to along with her attractive friends replace the USA team in France for a modeling tournament, however plane disaster strikes as the Van Burens are kicking off their annual Van Buren family getaway, the Overland Park Football team are called upon for a French football match, Deandra, Rachel, Judith, Saison, Little Brittnay and Lunch Lady Belinda are on a genuine French class field trip and Than has annoyingly just joined along for the ride.

episode of.title: The Most Popular Girls in School (TV Series 2012– )

2.plot: The Overland Park collective arrive in France, Mackenzie, Brittnay, Trisha and Trisha 2 press on to Jeanie Halverstad's offices and come into conflict with the French modeling team.

3.title: Nude Beach

episode of.title: The Most Popular Girls in School (TV Series 2012– )

3.plot: Mackenzie and Brittnay head to the French arts museum to recruit Deandra for the new Team USA, where Brittnay confronts Saison about her parents and French living, Lunch Lady Belinda reminisces on the Mona Lisa, Rachel attempts to offer herself for the modeling tournament. The Trishas head to recruit Than and the Overland Park football team who under Than's lead have come to a nude beach.

4.title: The New Team USA

episode of.title: The Most Popular Girls in School (TV Series 2012– )

4.plot: With the new Team USA assembled Mackenzie brings the collective back to Jeanie Halverstad for model training and the group displays their complete lack of preparation for the tournaments ahead.

5.title: Glow Up

episode of.title: The Most Popular Girls in School (TV Series 2012– )

5.plot: Shay Van Buren tries desperately join the new Team USA modeling team and upon rejection again finds solace in a new outlet, Jeanie and Mackenzie lead the team through photoshoots, Rachel and Judith fail at tailing Saison for Brittnay as a mysterious stranger enters the picture, Team USA gets a clothing upgrade.

6.title: Hand Modeling

episode of.title: The Most Popular Girls in School (TV Series 2012– )

6.plot: Team USA enters the hand modeling round of the competition but finds them not advancing, Deandra comes through and the night ends in many crazed drunken results as the French drunken age is brought upon them.

episode of.title: The Most Popular Girls in School (TV Series 2012– )

7.plot: The Team USA enters promotional advertising following the aftermath of their drunken celebratory night, Tanner tackles waking up in Than's bed and informing Tristan, Trisha 2, Matt, Cameron and Justin further sabotage the team's winning.

9.title: The Truth

episode of.title: The Most Popular Girls in School (TV Series 2012– )

9.plot: Saison departs to bring baby Brittany to meet her parents, Brittnay along with Deandra begin a pursuit so Brittnay can determine once for and all she is lying about her heritage.

10.plot: Brittnay and Deandra awaken the captives of the French modeling team to be force fed into obesity, Mackenzie dispatches the team into factions to retrieve Brittany for her round.

episode of.title: The Most Popular Girls in School (TV Series 2012– )

11.plot: Saison comes to the hand of the captive Brittnay and Deandra by seeking out Mackenzie and a mysterious recurring stranger. Judith and Rachel devise a way to help team USA as Brittnay suffers an ailment and Shay gives a shocking response.
